'''Figda''' was a type of sweet candy. As a matter of habit, [[Tru Veld/Legends|Tru Veld]] carried a bag of it in the pocket of his tunic sometime after becoming acquainted with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].

